Hi,

I'm an student studying engineering (with major as Computer Science) . I would like to get started on contributing to cargo and probably rust too.

I never worked with compilers are similar kinds of things before but I'm interested in doing systems programming and would like to get resources to learn about compilers architecture and such.

Looking forward to contribute more to cargo and other rust tools as well.
